oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Nashville's Night with Ben Folds and the Nashville Symphony Orchestra
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Folds, Ben, 1966-; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing Nashville's Night In, an annual fundraising event to support the Nashville Symphony, and featuring music by Ben Folds and the Nashville Symphony Orchestra. Poster features a woodcut. Poster is the first in a series.
